    .row(style=`background: yellowgreen`)
      .col.p-5
        .mb-4: h1.h1-home-white We Are Champions of a Healthy Internet
        p The Mozilla Networks brings together diverse leaders of all types. Join its ranks.

    .row.p-5
      .col-4
        h3
          a(href=`${env.virtualRoot}programs/fellowships`) Fellowships
      .col-4
        h3
          a(href=`${env.virtualRoot}programs/free-leadership-training`) Free Leadership Training
      .col-4
        h3
          a(href=`${env.virtualRoot}programs/internet-health-report`) Internet Health Report

    .row.my-5
      .col-6.p-5
        h3 Join Our Ranks
        p Access to bright minds, passionate community, and invaluable resources.
